mid\u2011range & luxury stays; otherwise \u20b980 at a caf\u00e9).  \\n\\n- **Morning**  \\n  - **Karur Museum** \u2013 exhibits on local history & textile art (\u20b950).  \\n  - **Shopping** \u2013 pick up authentic Karur silk sarees; budget \u20b92,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b94,000 for a decent piece.  \\n\\n- **Mid\u2011Morning Snack** \u2013 Fresh coconut water & banana (\u20b930).  \\n\\n- **Lunch** \u2013 \u201cMadhuram\u201d restaurant (non\u2011veg thali, \u20b9250\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9300).  \\n\\n- **Afternoon**  \\n  - Quick visit to **Kaveri River boat ride** (\u20b9150 per person).  \\n  - Return to hotel, check\u2011out.  \\n\\n- **Evening**  \\n  - Take a **taxi to Karur Railway Station** (\u2248\u202f\u20b9200).  \\n  - Board an **afternoon train** back to Chennai (or your departure city).  \\n\\n---\\n\\n### Approximate Cost Breakdown (per person)\\n\\n| Item | Budget (\u20b9) | Mid\u2011range (\u20b9) | Luxury (\u20b9) |\\n|------|------------|--------------|------------|\\n| Transport (train + local autos) | 1,200 \u2013 1,500 | 1,200 \u2013 1,500 | 1,200 \u2013 1,500 |\\n| Meals (2\u202fdays) | 1,200 \u2013 1,500 | 1,500 \u2013 2,000 | 2,000 \u2013 2,500 |\\n| Sightseeing & entry fees | 500 \u2013 700 | 500 \u2013 700 | 500 \u2013 700 |\\n| Hotel (2\u202fnights) | 2,400 \u2013 3,000 | 4,400 \u2013 5,600 | 9,000 \u2013 11,000 |\\n| Souvenirs (silk saree) | 2,000 \u2013 4,000 | 2,000 \u2013 4,000 | 2,000 \u2013 4,000 |\\n| **Total Approx.** | **\u2248\u202f\u20b97,300 \u2013 \u20b910,200** | **\u2248\u202f\u20b99,600 \u2013 \u20b913,800** | **\u2248\u202f\u20b914,200 \u2013\u202f\u20b919,700** |\\n\\nEven the luxury option stays well under the \u20b950,000 ceiling, leaving ample room for extra shopping, optional spa treatments, or a short stay in a nearby hill station.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Quick Tips  \\n- Book train tickets **30\u202fdays** in advance for best rates.  \\n- Carry cash for small vendors; most local shops accept only cash.  \\n- Dress modestly when visiting temples (shoulders & knees covered).  \\n- If you prefer a private ride, a **pre\u2011booked car** from Karur to Chennai costs \u2248\u202f\u20b93,500 \u2013 \u20b94,500.\\n\\nEnjoy a relaxed cultural immersion in Mayanoor, Karur!  \\n\\n**APPROVE**\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_81c3777c-0bc2-469b-b661-e187f9d4d352/81c3777c-0bc2-469b-b661-e187f9d4d352", "receiver": "output_topic_81c3777c-0bc2-469b-b661-e187f9d4d352/81c3777c-0bc2-469b-b661-e187f9d4d352", "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.SEND", "type": "Message"}
